    "name": "Vengful Remnant",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "You wreathe yourself in the tatters of all the souls claimed by your blade. Until the start of your next turn, you gain resistance 10 to all damage except force, *ghost touch*, spirit, and vitality, doubled if the source of the damage is non-magical. If you slay a significant foe not immune to spirit damage with your *spectral dagger* while under this effect, its duration increases until the end of your next turn.",
